com.ibm.team.process.common.advice

Interface IOperationConfigurationInfo

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IProcessConfigurationSource

    public interface IOperationConfigurationInfo
extends IProcessConfigurationSource
    An operation configuration info provides enough information for the server process to determine if an operation configuration is correct for a given time and place.

    This information can also be presented to end-users to explain how the lookup of permissions and behavior flowed.

    Since:
    0.6
